  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>This hotel is offered on a bed and breakfast basis.</p>
<p>Fuel up for a day skiing with the continental breakfast buffet served each day, consisting of cold cuts, pastries, bread and condiments.</p>
<p>The hotel is ideally situated close to some lovely restaurants serving a variety of different dishes. While you are away, be sure to try some of the regional cuisine, fondue and raclette is incredibly popular here. With Chamonix being so close to the Italian border, there is a good provision of Italian restaurants, so you don't have to look too far for a pizza.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
